*?BCDotShape: "currentpagedevice
/DeviceRenderingInfo 2 copy known
{ get
  /FastRip 2 copy known
  { get
    /dot 2 copy known
    { get }
    { pop pop (c) } ifelse
  }
  { pop pop (c) } ifelse
}
{ pop pop (c) } ifelse
= flush"
*End
*CloseUI: *BCDotShape
