*?BCGlobalDGC: "currentpagedevice
/DeviceRenderingInfo 2 copy known
{ get
  /FastRip 2 copy known
  { get
    /dgc 2 copy known
    { get }
    { pop pop (<none>) } ifelse
  }
  { pop pop (<none>) } ifelse
}
{ pop pop (<none>) } ifelse
= flush"
*End
*CloseUI: *BCGlobalDGC
*%
*%=========================================================
*% Automatic DGC
*%=========================================================
*%
*BCOpenUI *BCPressDGC/Automatic DGC: StringPickOne
*ParamBCPressDGC Group: "BCIntelliCurveFeatures/IntelliCurve"
*ParamBCPressDGC Default: none
*ParamBCPressDGC Format: %s
*ParamBCPressDGC InjectAt: Setup
*ParamBCPressDGC Inject: "
% string expected on top of stack with automatic DGC name in it !
/BCString exch def
[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /scrdgc
BCString >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*End
*BCCloseUI: *BCPressDGC

*OpenUI *BCPressDGC/Automatic DGC: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 DocumentSetup *BCPressDGC
*DefaultBCPressDGC: none
*BCPressDGC none/<3C>none<3E>: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /scrdgc
(<none>) >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*End

*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*% Add list of complex DGC strategies (.scrdgc and .icpro files) according to the examples below
*%
*% *BCPressDGC OtherInksLast.icpro: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /scrdgc
*% (OtherInksLast.icpro) >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*% *End
*% *BCPressDGC bobstcdi.scrdgc: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /scrdgc
*% (bobstcdi.scrdgc) >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*% *End
*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*BCPressDGC screened_proof.icpro: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /scrdgc
(screened_proof.icpro) >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*End

*?BCPressDGC: "currentpagedevice
/DeviceRenderingInfo 2 copy known
{ get
  /FastRip 2 copy known
  { get
    /scrdgc 2 copy known
    { get }
    { pop pop (<none>) } ifelse
  }
  { pop pop (<none>) } ifelse
}
{ pop pop (<none>) } ifelse
= flush"
*End
*CloseUI: *BCPressDGC
*%
*CloseGroup: *BCIntelliCurveFeatures
*%
*%
*%=========================================================
*% Feature Set: CDI LEN Output - Fixed (PixelClock and Perimeter both fixed)
*%=========================================================
*%
*OpenGroup: *BCCFOutputFeatures/CDI (F) LEN Output
*%
*%=========================================================
*% Configuration Set
*%=========================================================
*%
*OpenUI *BCConfiguration/Configuration Set: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 DocumentSetup *BCConfiguration

*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*% Add default configuration set (must exist in the list !) and list of configuration sets according to the example below
*%
*% *DefaultBCConfiguration: 352_x_689_pos
*% *BCConfiguration 352_x_689_pos: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /conf
*% (352_x_689_pos) >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*% *End
*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*DefaultBCConfiguration: conf1
*BCConfiguration conf1: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /conf
(conf1) >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*End
*BCConfiguration conf2: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /conf
(conf2) >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*End
*BCConfiguration maxsize: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /conf
(maxsize) >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*End

*?BCConfiguration: "currentpagedevice
/DeviceRenderingInfo 2 copy known
{ get
  /FastRip 2 copy known
  { get
    /conf 2 copy known
    { get }
    { pop pop (352_x_689_pos) } ifelse
  }
  { pop pop (352_x_689_pos) } ifelse
}
{ pop pop (352_x_689_pos) } ifelse
= flush"
*End
*CloseUI: *BCConfiguration
*%
*%=========================================================
*% Resolution
*%=========================================================
*%
*OpenUI *Resolution/Resolution: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 11 DocumentSetup *Resolution
*ParamResolution Tag: "   (Approx.)"

*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*% Add default resolution (must exist in the list !) and list of resolutions according to the example below
*%
*% *DefaultResolution: 600dpi
*% *Resolution 600dpi: "1 dict dup /HWResolution [600.00 600.00] put setpagedevice"
*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*DefaultResolution: 2000dpi
*Resolution 2000dpi: "1 dict dup /HWResolution [2000 2000] put setpagedevice"
*Resolution 2100dpi: "1 dict dup /HWResolution [2100 2100] put setpagedevice"
*Resolution 2400dpi: "1 dict dup /HWResolution [2400 2400] put setpagedevice"
*Resolution 2540dpi: "1 dict dup /HWResolution [2540 2540] put setpagedevice"
*Resolution 2800dpi: "1 dict dup /HWResolution [2800 2800] put setpagedevice"
*Resolution 4000dpi: "1 dict dup /HWResolution [4000 4000] put setpagedevice"

*?Resolution: "=string 0 [ currentpagedevice /HWResolution get aload pop 2 copy
eq {pop cvi} {cvi exch cvi exch (x) exch} ifelse (dpi) ] {3 copy pop 1 index length 1 index sub
getinterval cvs length add} forall 0 exch getinterval cvn = flush"
*End

*CloseUI: *Resolution
*%
*%=========================================================
*% PixelClock
*%=========================================================
*%
*OpenUI *BCPixelClock/PixelClock: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 DocumentSetup *BCPixelClock

*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*% Add default pixelclock and single pixelclock according to the example below
*%
*% *DefaultBCPixelClock: 360000
*% *BCPixelClock 360000: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /pixelclock
*% 360000 >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*% *End
*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*DefaultBCPixelClock: 0
*BCPixelClock 0: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /pixelclock 0 >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*End

*CloseUI: *BCPixelClock
*%
*%=========================================================
*% Perimeter
*%=========================================================
*%
*OpenUI *BCPerimeter/Perimeter: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 DocumentSetup *BCPerimeter

*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*% Add default perimeter and single perimeter according to the example below
*%
*% *DefaultBCPerimeter: 1023.45
*% *BCPerimeter 1023.45 { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /perimeter
*% 1023.45 >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*% *End
*%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
*DefaultBCPerimeter: 0
*BCPerimeter 0/0: "[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /perimeter 0 >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped cleartomark"
*End

*CloseUI: *BCPerimeter
*%
*%=========================================================
*% Output File Name
*%=========================================================
*%
*BCOpenUI *BCOutputName/Output File Name: String
*OrderDependency: 20 DocumentSetup *BCOutputName
*%ParamBCOutputName Default: ----- no default output file name, so commented out ..
*ParamBCOutputName Default: ""
*ParamBCOutputName Group: "BCCFOutputFeatures/CDI (F) LEN Output"
*ParamBCOutputName Format: %s
*ParamBCOutputName InjectAt: Setup
*ParamBCOutputName Inject: "
% string expected on top of stack with output file name in it !
dup length 0 eq {pop}{/BCString exch def
[ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /output BCString >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped pop cleartomark} ifelse"
*End
*?BCOutputName: "currentpagedevice
/DeviceRenderingInfo 2 copy known
{ get
  /FastRip 2 copy known
  { get
    /output 2 copy known
    { get }
    { pop pop () } ifelse
  }
  { pop pop () } ifelse
}
{ pop pop () } ifelse
= flush"
*End
*BCCloseUI: *BCOutputName
*%
*CloseGroup: *BCCFOutputFeatures
*%
*%=========================================================
*% Feature Set: Output Options
*%=========================================================
*%
*OpenGroup: *BCOutputOptions/Output Options
*%
*%=========================================================
*% FlexRip Version
*%=========================================================
*%
*OpenUI *BCFRipVersion/FlexRip Version: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 DocumentSetup *BCFRipVersion
*DefaultBCFRipVersion: FRip70
*BCFRipVersion FRip70/FlexRip 7.0: "
  [ { << /DeviceRenderingInfo << /Type 0 /FastRip << /serverversion /FR7.0 >> >> >> setpagedevice } stopped
  cleartomark"
*End
*CloseUI: *BCFRipVersion
*%
*%=========================================================
*% Save To File
*%=========================================================
*%
*BCOpenUI *BCSaveAs/Save as File: SaveAsFile
*OrderDependency: 10 DocumentSetup *BCSaveAs
*ParamBCSaveAs Group: "BCOutputOptions/Output Options"
*ParamBCSaveAs ChooseLabel: "Browse ..."
*BCCloseUI: *BCSaveAs
*%
*CloseGroup: *BCOutputOptions
*%

*% Halftone Information ===============
*DefaultHalftoneType: 1
*ScreenFreq: "150"
*ScreenAngle: "75"
*%
*ResScreenFreq 2000dpi: "150"
*ResScreenAngle 2000dpi: "75"
*ResScreenFreq 2100dpi: "150"
*ResScreenAngle 2100dpi: "75"
*ResScreenFreq 2400dpi: "150"
*ResScreenAngle 2400dpi: "75"
*ResScreenFreq 2540dpi: "150"
*ResScreenAngle 2540dpi: "75"
*ResScreenFreq 2800dpi: "150"
*ResScreenAngle 2800dpi: "75"
*ResScreenFreq 4000dpi: "150"
*ResScreenAngle 4000dpi: "75"
*%
*DefaultScreenProc: Dot
*ScreenProc Dot: "{pop}"

*DefaultTransfer: Null
*Transfer Null: "{ }"
*Transfer Null.Inverse: "{ 1 exch sub }"

*% Paper Handling ===================
*% Use these entries to set paper size most of the time, unless there is
*% specific reason to use PageRegion.
*OpenUI *PageSize: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 30 DocumentSetup *PageSize
*DefaultPageSize: A4
*PageSize A1: "<< /PageSize [1684 2384] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize A1.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [1684 2384] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize A2: "<< /PageSize [1191 1684] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize A2.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [1191 1684] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize A3: "<< /PageSize [842 1191] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize A3.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [842 1191] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize A4: "<< /PageSize [595 842] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize A4.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [595 842] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize B4: "<< /PageSize [729 1032] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize B4.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [729 1032] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize B5: "<< /PageSize [516 729] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize B5.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [516 729] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize EnvC5: "<< /PageSize [459 649] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize EnvC5.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [459 649] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Legal: "<< /PageSize [612 1008] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Legal.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [612 1008] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Letter: "<< /PageSize [612 792] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Letter.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [612 792] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Tabloid: "<< /PageSize [792 1224] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Tabloid.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [792 1224] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Ledger: "<< /PageSize [1224 792] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Ledger.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [1224 792] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Env10: "<< /PageSize [297 684] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Env10.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [297 684] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize EnvDL: "<< /PageSize [312 624] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize EnvDL.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [312 624] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Executive: "<< /PageSize [522 756] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Executive.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [522 756] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize EnvMonarch: "<< /PageSize [279 540] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize EnvMonarch.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [279 540] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize CDI3000x3000mm: "<< /PageSize [8503 8503] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize CDI3000x3000mm.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [8503 8503] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Max: "<< /PageSize [8503 8503] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageSize Max.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [8503 8503] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
*?PageSize: "3 dict begin /TheDict << 1 <<
	/A1.Transverse [1684 2384]
	/A2.Transverse [1191 1684]
	/A3.Transverse [842 1191]
	/A4.Transverse [595 842]
	/B4.Transverse [729 1032]
	/B5.Transverse [516 729]
	/EnvC5.Transverse [459 649]
	/Legal.Transverse [612 1008]
	/Letter.Transverse [612 792]
	/Tabloid.Transverse [792 1224]
	/Ledger.Transverse [1224 792]
	/Env10.Transverse [297 684]
	/EnvDL.Transverse [312 624]
	/Executive.Transverse [522 756]
	/EnvMonarch.Transverse [279 540]
	/CDI3000x3000mm.Transverse [8503 8503]
	/Max.Transverse [8503 8503]
>> 0 <<
	/A1 [1684 2384]
	/A2 [1191 1684]
	/A3 [842 1191]
	/A4 [595 842]
	/B4 [729 1032]
	/B5 [516 729]
	/EnvC5 [459 649]
	/Legal [612 1008]
	/Letter [612 792]
	/Tabloid [792 1224]
	/Ledger [1224 792]
	/Env10 [297 684]
	/EnvDL [312 624]
	/Executive [522 756]
	/EnvMonarch [279 540]
	/CDI3000x3000mm [8503 8503]
	/Max [8503 8503]
>> >> def
/TheOrientation currentpagedevice /Orientation get def
/ThePageSize currentpagedevice /PageSize get def
TheDict TheOrientation known
{/Unknown TheDict TheOrientation get {aload pop ThePageSize aload pop 3 -1
roll eq 3 1 roll eq and {exch pop exit} {pop} ifelse} forall} {/Unknown} ifelse
= flush end"
*End

*CloseUI: *PageSize

*% These entries will set up the frame buffer. Usually used with manual feed.
*OpenUI *PageRegion: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 40 DocumentSetup *PageRegion
*DefaultPageRegion: A4
*PageRegion A1: "<< /PageSize [1684 2384] /Orientation 0 >> setpagedevice"
*PageRegion A1.Transverse: "<< /PageSize [1684 2384] /Orientation 1 >> setpagedevice"
