*%=== Custom Page Sizes ==================================

*% These entries provide the code and parameter ranges for a user
*% to set up a custom page size.
*CustomPageSize True: "
exch pop exch pop
dup 2 mod 0 eq
{ 3 1 roll exch 3 -1 roll } if
dup 0 eq { pop 3 } { 1 sub } ifelse
<<
    /Orientation 3 -1 roll
    /PageSize [ 7 -2 roll ]
>> setpagedevice"
*End

*ParamCustomPageSize Width: 1 points 1 8503
*ParamCustomPageSize Height: 2 points 1 8503
*ParamCustomPageSize WidthOffset/Margins: 3 points 0 0
*ParamCustomPageSize HeightOffset: 4 points 0 0
*ParamCustomPageSize Orientation: 5 int 0 1
*MaxMediaWidth: "8503.0"
*MaxMediaHeight: "8503.0"

*CenterRegistered: False
*DefaultLeadingEdge: PreferLong
*LeadingEdge Short: ""
*LeadingEdge Long: ""
*LeadingEdge PreferLong: ""

