*% Status (format: %%[ status: <one of these> ]%% )
*Status: "idle"
*Status: "busy"
*Status: "waiting"
*Status: "printing"
*Status: "warming up"
*Status: "PrinterError: out of paper or end of ribbon"
*Status: "PrinterError: printer fault"
*Status: "PrinterError: printer offline"

*% Printer Error (format: %%[ PrinterError: <one of these> ]%%)
